videoSnippet.title: The Knight is Coming! | Nakamura vs Karjakin | Norway Championship 2018 | Round 8
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Check out agadmator's chess Channel Song here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ApkShmA65qg&t=3s

Hikaru Nakamura vs Sergey Karjakin
Altibox Norway (2018), rd 8, Jun-06 
English Opening: Four Knights (A29)

1. c4 Nf6 2. Nc3 e5 3. Nf3 Nc6 4. g3 Bb4 5. Bg2 O-O 6. O-O e4 7. Ng5 Bxc3 8. bxc3 Re8 9. f3 exf3 10. Nxf3 d5 11. d4 dxc4 12. Bg5 h6 13. Bxf6 Qxf6 14. Nd2 Qe7 15. e4 Na5 16. e5 Be6 17. Ne4 Rad8 18. Qh5 b5 19. Nf6+ Kh8 20. d5 Bxd5 21. Bxd5 Rxd5 22. Nxe8 Rxe5 23. Qxf7 Qxe8 24. Qxe8+ Rxe8 25. Rae1 Rxe1 26. Rxe1 c5 27. Kf2 b4 28. Ke3 bxc3 29. Rc1 Nc6 30. Rxc3 Nb4 31. Rxc4 Nxa2 32. Rxc5 Nb4 33. Ke4 Kh7 34. Rc4 a5 35. Rc5 a4 36. Ra5 Nc6 37. Rxa4 Nd8 38. Ra6 Nf7 39. Kf5 Nh8 40. h4 Nf7 41. g4
